quote><blockquote>屌..鴻乜撚野興..<br />\n做牛腩做到成條柴都仲咁多人去食<br />\n個麵又細又重鹼味<br />\n個湯唔知有乜味仲要食完好渴<br />\n時不時仲會有架屎車隊入間鋪抽屎..臭到仆街<br />\n去隔離合興仲好啦起碼牛腩位都有三種</blockquote><br />\n好耐無食鴻興，唔想煮飯就去合興買，平啲又大碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，鴻興應該得合興一半份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n合興仲有牛沙瓜，鴻興乜都冇就叫自己牛雜專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efdc1e791be4a8242f739f0b60c3281bb1feef0","tid":338883,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寶林街市同富寧鴻興嘅牛腩牛雜都好高質<br />\n新都城三才雖然自家製但轉型前d 粉麵都普通<br />\n係魚旦墨魚條幾好<br />\n所以依家變左淨係賣丸嘅工場都唔太可惜</blockquote><br />\n聽d師奶講，間野d丸自己打<br />\n<br />\n要排隊買"},{"pid":"9c965a8e4c3b584c61e154d10b966353a855a1d5","tid":338883,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T14:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洪興牛腩<br />\n寶林街市粉仔</blockquote><br />\n粉仔堅正</blockquote><br />\n粉仔細細個就食，個個食過都話正<br />\n我就覺得好普通，可能我唔太好粉麵"},{"pid":"60b6cf7c5afbd1268ac1d4208e1dd8102e38ff5c","tid":338883,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T14:16:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慧安園煎餃</blockquote><br />\n好難食 又硬又銀胃<br />\n八方雲集啲垃圾都好食過佢"},{"pid":"92f8d2e2af8c2071b1c6097cb4368b65b26b10ce","tid":338883,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"寶林呢個鐘數真係無野食"},{"pid":"b5d695ece3d0e21e1ef40644ad63adeb45bedfe1","tid":338883,"uid":88282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T14:22:48.000Z","msg":"仲未有人講 寶琳街巿 利泰?? <br />\n定還是我太劣....."},{"pid":"e562540f79764a45f62e1c87b72a3f38420a3e1f","tid":338883,"uid":115165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:49:50.000Z","msg":"寶林街市有間粉仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a